

=Bio=

Research fellow at the  Institute of Science and Environmental Technology (ICTA) of Autonomous  University Barcelona, project manager of the ENTITLE, an EU FP7 Initial  Training Network under the Marie Curie actions.  His research interests include: environmental economics, ecological  economics, sustainable development, public goods, commons, social  metabolism, environmental conflicts, and water security. He is also also part of the R&D Barcelona group exploring the idea of de-growth, i.e. a smooth disappearing of the hipertrophic modern individual.


